articles.title: Australian Man Breaks Guinness World Record With 3,206 Push-Ups In An Hour - Times Now
articles.description: An Australian man has broken the Guinness World Record for ‘most push ups in one hour’. Lucas Helmke, 33, of Brisbane, Australia, performed 3,206 push-ups in an hour to claim the Guinness World Records title, with an incredible average of 53 per minute. The b…
articles.content: Lucas Helmke, of Brisbane, Australia, performed 3,206 push-ups to earn the Guinness World Record title for most pushups in one hour | Guinness World Records
